# Object Property: pbpko:BFO_0000062 (preceded by)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:BFO_0000062 "x is preceded by y if and only if the time point at which y ends is before or equivalent to the time point at which x starts. Formally: x preceded by y iff ω(y) <= α(x), where α is a function that maps a process to a start point, and ω is a function that maps a process to an end point."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:BFO_0000062 "preceded by"@en)
SubObjectPropertyOf(pbpko:BFO_0000062 pbpko:RO_0002086)
InverseObjectProperties(pbpko:BFO_0000062 pbpko:BFO_0000063)
TransitiveObjectProperty(pbpko:BFO_0000062)
ObjectPropertyDomain(pbpko:BFO_0000062 pbpko:BFO_0000003)
ObjectPropertyRange(pbpko:BFO_0000062 pbpko:BFO_0000003)

