# Object Property: pbpko:RO_0002013 (has regulatory component activity)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:RO_0002013 "A 'has regulatory component activity' B if A and B are GO molecular functions (GO_0003674), A has_component B and A is regulated by B.")
