# Object Property: pbpko:RO_0002014 (has negative regulatory component activity)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:RO_0002014 "A relationship that holds between a GO molecular function and a component of that molecular function that negatively regulates the activity of the whole.  More formally, A 'has regulatory component activity' B iff :A and B are GO molecular functions (GO_0003674), A has_component B and A is negatively regulated by B.")
